cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with formulating a top-k query and developing efficient index structures to answer it. This is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed scoring function combines attractive and repulsive dimensions, which is a concept used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses empirical evaluation and qualitative analysis, which are common in data science (cs.DS).
